definitions.definition: A flattened portion of ground meat or a vegetarian equivalent, usually round but sometimes square in shape.
examples: The cook fried the hamburger patty , then put it in a bun.

definitions.definition: A pastry with various fillings and spices baked inside a flaky shell , often tinted golden yellow with an egg yolk mixture or turmeric .

main_definition: ( US, Australia, New Zealand ) A flattened portion of ground meat or a vegetarian equivalent, usually round but sometimes square in shape.
secondary_definitions: ( Jamaica ) A pastry with various fillings and spices baked inside a flaky shell , often tinted golden yellow with an egg yolk mixture or turmeric .
( England, strictly MLE ) A foolish or stupid person.
